<div class="container-narrow">
    <h1>About DLSU Eats</h1>

    <div class="restaurant-detail">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>DLSU Eats was created by students, for students. Born from countless lunch debates about where to eat near campus, we wanted to build a platform where the DLSU community could share their honest dining experiences and discover the best eats around the university.</p>
        <p>Whether you're a freshman looking for affordable meals, a grad student seeking study-friendly cafes, or just someone who loves good food, DLSU Eats is here to help you find your next favorite restaurant.</p>

        <hr>

        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <h3>Comprehensive Restaurant Database</h3>
        <p>Browse through dozens of restaurants near DLSU, from budget-friendly fast food to special occasion dining. Each listing includes location, price range, food styles, hours, and contact information.</p>
        <h3>Authentic Student Reviews</h3>
        <p>Read honest reviews from fellow DLSU students and community members. Our reviews focus on what matters most: taste, value, atmosphere, and service.</p>
        <h3>Smart Search and Filters</h3>
        <p>Find exactly what you're craving with our powerful search and filtering tools. Filter by cuisine type, price range, rating, and more.</p>
        <h3>Community Engagement</h3>
        <p>Mark reviews as helpful, see top-rated reviews, and connect with other food enthusiasts in the DLSU community.</p>

        <hr>

