        <h2>Our Values</h2>
        <h3>Authenticity</h3>
        <p>We value genuine experiences. Every review on DLSU Eats should reflect a real visit and honest opinion.</p>
        <h3>Community</h3>
        <p>We're built for the DLSU community, by the DLSU community. Supporting local businesses while helping students make informed dining decisions.</p>
        <h3>Respect</h3>
        <p>We foster constructive dialogue. Critical reviews are welcome, but personal attacks and disrespectful behavior are not.</p>
        <h3>Transparency</h3>
        <p>Restaurant owners can respond to reviews, and users should disclose any conflicts of interest.</p>

        <hr>

